      "role": "user",
      "content": "a phase? it doesn't feel like a phase. it feels like the air has been sucked out of the room. ten years... we built an entire life together and now it's just gone. i look at the apartment and it's like i'm a ghost in my own house. i don't think i'm \"stronger than i think.\" i think i'm just empty. i don't see any version of the future where this doesn't hurt this much.",
